OL,3,CClosure of blast furnaces would leave
OL,4,CUK underprepared for war, warn unions
OL,6,FThe UK would be "woefully
OL,7,Funderprepared" for potential wars if
OL,8,Ftwo blast furnaces close, according to
OL,9,Fthe GMB Union.
OL,11,FIn a letter written to the UK, the
OL,12,Funion warned that the "UK will be
OL,13,Funable to make full range of steel
OL,14,Fneeded for warships and other parts of
OL,15,Fdefence supply chain."
OL,17,FOn Friday, 19 January, announced it
OL,18,Fwould close both of Port Talbot's
OL,19,Fblast furnaces in an attempt cut costs
OL,20,Fat the plant and move toward greener
OL,21,Fsteel production.
