OL,3,CClosure of blast furnaces would leave
OL,4,CUK underprepared for war, warn unions
OL,6,FUnder Tata's new plans, the plant will
OL,7,Fnot be able to create 'virgin' steel,
OL,8,Finstead it will use an electric arc
OL,9,Ffurnaces to melt scrap steel.
OL,11,FThe GMB Union says it is vital that
OL,12,Fthe country can produce virgin steel
OL,13,Fin order to build warships and other
OL,14,Fparts of the defence industry.
OL,16,FMatt Roberts, GMB national officer,
OL,17,Fsaid: "We live in a turbulent global
OL,18,Fenvironment.
