OL,3,CClosure of blast furnaces would leave
OL,4,CUK underprepared for war, warn unions
OL,6,F"Both Nato's defence chief and Mr
OL,7,FShapps himself have warned that war in
OL,8,Fthe next two decades is a possibility.
OL,10,F"Yet we are on the brink of losing our
OL,11,Ffull ability to make our own steel,
OL,12,Fvital to our defence industry, not
OL,13,Fleast in building warships.
OL,15,F"It's utter folly.
OL,17,F"GMB is very clear, we must retain
OL,18,Fsovereign capability to make virgin
OL,19,Fsteel."
