OL,6,FTata bosses are due to appear before
OL,7,FMPs next week to answer questions
OL,8,Fabout the Indian multinational
OL,9,Fcompany's decision to shut down the
OL,10,FPort Talbot blast furnaces.
OL,12,FOn Wednesday, Tata Steel's chief
OL,13,Fexecutive Rajesh Nair and Thachat
OL,14,FViswanath Narendran, the global chief
OL,15,Fexecutive and managing director, are
OL,16,Fscheduled to give evidence to the
OL,17,FWelsh Affairs Select Committee.
